criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Diagnosis of acute pancreatitis (Atlanta standard), abdominal pain occurred within one
             week of admission;

          2. APACHEII score is more than 8 and Ranson score is greater than 3;

          3. Age 18-75;

          4. Obtaining informed consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Pregnancy pancreatitis;

          2. Patients with the following disease history: severe cardiac, pulmonary, renal, liver
             function insufficiency or immunodeficiency disease.
